discovery.service

Class CityManagerWebService

  • java.lang.Object
    • discovery.service.ServiceDescription
      • discovery.service.AvailableService
        • discovery.service.CityManagerWebService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CityManager

    public class CityManagerWebService
extends AvailableService
implements CityManager
    This class represent a city manager, it can
    • add a city
    • remove a city
    • return the list of cities
    • search a city with a given name
    • search a city at a position
    • return the list of cities near 10km of the given position
    Author:
    Folabi & Caron & Saval.
